Signed-off-by: Srinivasa Rao Mandadapu <srivasam@codeaurora.org>
Reviewed-by: Srinivas Kandagatla <srinivas.kandagatla@linaro.org>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20210604154545.1198337-1-judyhsiao@chromium.org
